==English==

===Verb form===
'''training'''
# [[present participle]] of the verb ''to [[train]]''

===Noun===
'''training'''

# [[action]] of the verb ''to [[train]]''.
# the activity of [[imparting]] and [[acquiring]] [[skill]]s.
# the result of good [[social]] [[upbringing]].
#{{computing}} the process by which two [[modem]]s determine which [[protocol]] and [[speed]] to use; [[handshaking]].
#(''voice recognition'') the [[recording]] of [[multiple]] [[sample]]s of a [[user]]'s [[voice]] to aid [[pattern]] [[recognition]].

